  <li>Writing <code>5.0</code> instead of <code>0.05</code> for the interest rate</li>
  <li>Forgetting the parentheses in <code>(1 + interest_rate)</code></li>
  <li>Using <code>*</code> instead of <code>**</code> when applying the number of years</li>
  <li>Printing the wrong variable name or a misspelled variable</li>
</ul>
      ]]></text>
